INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (15,'Men\'s Better Sweater® 1/4-Zip Fleece','A warm, low-bulk quarter-zip jacket made of soft, sweater-knit recycled polyester fleece. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">100% Recycled Polyester Sweater-Knit Fleece</h2>\nMade of 100% recycled polyester fleece with a sweater-knit face, fleece interior and heathered yarns\n</li>\n\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Quarter-Zip with Stand-Up Collar</h2>\nQuarter-zip design with a zip-through stand-up collar for warmth and soft comfort\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Raglan Sleeve Construction</h2>\nThe raglan sleeve design allows full shoulder and arm mobility and reduces chafing under pack straps\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Zippered Left-Chest Pocket</h2>\n\nZippered left-chest pocket holds a phone or audio device\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Skin-Friendly Cuffs and Hem</h2>\n\nShape-holding micropolyester-jersey trim at the cuffs and hem feels smooth and soft on the skin and provides added abrasion resistance\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Flat-Seam Construction</h2>\nCrafted with flat-seam stitching to reduce both bulk and chafing\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Supporting the People Who Made This Product</h2>\nHip length; Fair Trade Certified™ sewn, which means the people who made it earned a premium for their labor\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Thailand.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n505 g (17.8 oz)\n</li>\n','\n<li>10-oz 100% recycled polyester knitted fleece dyed with a low-impact process that significantly reduces the use of dyestuffs, energy and water compared to conventional dyeing methods</li><li>Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,99.00,1),(16,'Men\'s Nano-Air® Hoody','The Nano-Air® Hoody was made to be worn for the entirety of your aerobic, start-stop alpine missions, so you’re never slowed down by changing layers. Warm, stretchy and breathable FullRange® insulation dumps excess heat when you’re working hard and keeps you warm when you’re not. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Stretchy, Breathable, Weather-Resistant Fabric</h2>\n100% polyester (87% recycled) plain-weave shell and lining fabric offers generous mechanical stretch, exceptional breathability and improved abrasion resistance; microtexture creates excellent next-to-skin comfort; features a DWR (durable water repellent) finish\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Revolutionary FullRange Insulation</h2>\nRevolutionary 60-g FullRange® insulation (40% recycled) warms and stretches and, combined with the shell and lining, supplies outstanding mechanical stretch and unprecedented air permeability (40CFM), allowing excess heat to move away from the body\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Designed for Freedom of Movement</h2>\n\nStretch fabrics and insulation, articulated patterning, and strategically placed, low-profile quilting provide exceptional range of motion for unhindered movement\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Stretchy Hood</h2>\n\nStretchy hood with binding easily pulls on or off, even when jacket is zipped\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Center-Front Zipper</h2>\nCenter-front zipper has zipper garage at chin for next-to-skin comfort\n</li>\n\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Pocket Features</h2>\nTwo handwarmer pockets and a left-chest pocket are zippered, low-profile and low-bulk to wear comfortably with a harness or pack; self-stuffs into left-chest pocket\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Low-Profile Variable Conditions Cuffs</h2>\nSleek, low-bulk, snag-resistant Variable Conditions Cuffs use stretch knit for versatile coverage and comfort; elasticized hem seals in warmth; Fair Trade Certified™ sewn\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Vietnam.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n346 g (12.2 oz)\n</li>\n','\n<li>Shell and lining: 1.7-oz 100% polyester (87% recycled) plain weave with four-way mechanical stretch and a DWR (durable water repellent) finish</li><li>Cuffs: 4.9-oz 100% polyester snag-resistant stretch knit with a DWR finish</li><li>Insulation: 60-g FullRange® 100% polyester (40% recycled) with four-way stretch</li><li>Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,299.00,2),(17,'Men\'s Classic Synchilla® Fleece Vest','Classic vest made with tried-and-true midweight Synchilla® polyester fleece. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">100% Recycled Polyester Fleece</h2>\n\nMade of 100% recycled polyester double-sided fleece with an anti-pilling finish\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Full-Length Zipper with Stand-up Collar</h2>\nFull-front zip with a zip-through stand-up collar to protect your neck\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Offset Shoulder Seams</h2>\nDesigned with offset shoulder seams for pack-wearing comfort and long-lasting durability\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Pocket Details</h2>\n\nZippered left-chest pocket and two zippered handwarmer pockets hold your essentials\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Hip Length</h2>\nThe hip length provides additional coverage and pairs well with a hipbelt or harness\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Supporting the People Who Made This Product</h2>\nFair Trade Certified™ sewn, which means the people who made it earned a premium for their labor\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Nicaragua and El Salvador.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n315 g (11.1 oz)\n</li>\n','\n<li>Body: 8-oz 100% recycled polyester double-sided fleece with an anti-pilling finish</li><li>Pocket bags: 3-oz 100% polyester warp-knit brushed mesh</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,79.00,1),(18,'Men\'s Nano Puff® Vest','Warm, windproof, water-resistant—the Nano Puff® Vest uses incredibly lightweight and highly compressible 60-g PrimaLoft® Gold Insulation Eco with 55% postconsumer recycled content, wrapped in a 100% recycled polyester shell and lining. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">100% Recycled Shell Fabric</h2>\nLightweight 100% recycled polyester ripstop shell and lining fabric has a DWR (durable water repellent) finish\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">55% Recycled Insulation</h2>\n\n60-g PrimaLoft® Gold Insulation Eco, with 55% postconsumer recycled content, is water-repellent, highly compressible and maintains 98% of warmth, even when wet\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Horizontal Quilting Pattern</h2>\n\nBrick quilting pattern with horizontal quilt lines on side panels stabilizes insulation and uses durable thread for abrasion resistance\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Center-Front Zipper</h2>\nCenter-front zipper has wicking interior storm flap and zipper garage at chin for next-to-skin comfort\n</li>\n\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Pocket Features</h2>\nTwo zippered handwarmer pockets have cleanly finished zipper garages; zippered internal chest pocket doubles as a stuffsack with a reinforced carabiner clip-in loop\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Sealed-In Warmth</h2>\nDrawcord-adjustable drop-tail hem seals in warmth\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Fair Trade Sewn</h2>\n\nFair Trade Certified™ sewn\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Vietnam.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n227 g (8 oz)\n</li>\n','\n<li>Shell: 1.4-oz 20-denier 100% recycled polyester with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish</li><li>Lining: 1.3-oz 22-denier 100% recycled polyester with a DWR finish</li><li>Insulation: 60-g PrimaLoft® Gold Insulation Eco 100% polyester (55% postconsumer recycled content)</li><li>Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,149.00,1),(19,'Men\'s R2® TechFace Hoody','The perfect cold-weather crosslayer, our R2® TechFace Hoody provides warmth and breathability with the added benefits of abrasion and weather resistance for extended versatility in shifting mountain conditions. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">High-Loft Warmth with Durable Face Fabric</h2>\n\nHigh-loft double-weave fabric is soft and warm next to skin but doesn’t trap heat; face is durable and treated with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish to shed moisture\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Under-the-helmet hood construction is light and simple</h2>\nUnder-the-helmet hood with elastic binding is warm and simple\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Pocket Features</h2>\nOne left-chest pocket and two high handwarmer pockets are clean-finished and harness- and pack-compatible; two interior drop-in pockets\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Low-Profile Variable Conditions Cuffs</h2>\n\nSleek, low-bulk, snag-resistant cuffs with stretch knit provide versatile coverage and comfort\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Sealed-In Warmth</h2>\nPartial binding on hem seals in warmth\n</li>\n\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Fair Trade Sewn</h2>\nFair Trade Certified™ sewn\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Vietnam.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n485 g (17.1 oz)\n</li>\n\n','\n<li>7.6-oz 94% polyester (77% recycled)/6% spandex breathable stretch double weave with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish</li><li>Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,189.00,2),(20,'Men\'s Better Sweater® Fleece Vest','A warm, low-bulk full-zip vest made of soft, sweater-knit recycled polyester fleece. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">100% Recycled Polyester Sweater-Knit Fleece</h2>\n\nMade of 100% recycled polyester fleece with a sweater-knit face, fleece interior and heathered yarns\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Full-Zip with Stand-Up Collar</h2>\nThe full-zip design features a zip-through stand-up collar to protect your neck\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Offset Shoulder Seams</h2>\nDesigned with offset shoulder seams for pack-wearing comfort and long-lasting durability\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Pocket Details</h2>\n\nA zippered left-chest pocket and two zippered handwarmer pockets hold your items and protect your hands\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Shape-Holding Armholes and Hem</h2>\nThe armholes and hem are trimmed with shape-holding micropolyester jersey\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Flat-Seam Construction</h2>\nFlat-seam stitching reduces both bulk and chafing; hip length\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Supporting the People Who Made This Product</h2>\nFair Trade Certified™ sewn, which means the people who made it earned a premium for their labor\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Sri Lanka.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n394 g (13.9 oz)\n</li>\n','\n<li>10-oz 100% recycled polyester knitted fleece dyed with a low-impact process that significantly reduces the use of dyestuffs, energy and water compared to conventional dyeing methods</li><li>Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,99.00,1),(21,'Men\'s Rainshadow Jacket','For long days on the trail, our Rainshadow Jacket is lightweight and stretchy, using 3-layer H2No® Performance Standard technology for exceptional waterproof/breathable performance, unrestricted mobility, and all-day comfort. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Stretch 3-Layer H2No Performance Standard Shell</h2>\nStretch 3-layer waterproof/breathable H2No® Performance Standard shell provides unrestricted mobility, the highest levels of comfort and performance, and long-term waterproof durability\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Adjustable Hood</h2>\nTwo-way-adjustable hood with a laminated visor rolls down and stows with a simplified cord-and-hook design\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Watertight Zippers</h2>\n\nCoated, watertight center-front zipper and welted, venting pit zips are treated with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Pocket Features</h2>\n Exterior left-chest pocket with coated, watertight zipper, and welted handwarmer pockets have DWR-treated zips\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Self-Stuffs into Chest Pocket</h2>\nSelf-stuffs into left-front pocket with carabiner clip-in loop\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Hook-and-Loop Closures</h2>\nMinimal self-fabric hook-and-loop cuff closures\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Adjustable Hem</h2>\nDual-adjust drawcord hem seals out weather; Fair Trade Certified™ sewn\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Vietnam.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n397 g (14 oz)\n</li>\n','\n<li>H2No® Performance Standard shell: 3-layer, 3.2-oz 30-denier ECONYL® 100% recycled nylon stretch ripstop face, polycarbonate PU membrane with 13% bio-based content, a tricot backer and a DWR (durable water repellent) finish</li><li>Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,199.00,1),(22,'Men\'s Nano Puff® Hoody','Warm, windproof, water-resistant—the Nano Puff® Hoody uses incredibly lightweight and highly compressible 60-g PrimaLoft® Gold Insulation Eco with 55% postconsumer recycled content, wrapped in a 100% recycled polyester shell and lining. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">100% Recycled Shell Fabric</h2>\nLightweight 100% recycled polyester ripstop shell and lining fabric has a DWR (durable water repellent) finish\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">55% Recycled Insulation</h2>\n\n60-g PrimaLoft® Gold Insulation Eco, with 55% postconsumer recycled content, is water-repellent, highly compressible and maintains 98% of warmth, even when wet\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Horizontal Quilting Pattern</h2>\n\nBrick quilting pattern with horizontal quilt lines on side panels stabilizes insulation and uses durable thread for abrasion resistance\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Center-Front Zipper</h2>\nCenter-front zipper has wicking interior storm flap and zipper garage at chin for next-to-skin comfort\n</li>\n\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Pocket Features</h2>\nTwo zippered handwarmer pockets have cleanly finished zipper garages; zippered internal chest pocket doubles as a stuffsack with a reinforced carabiner clip-in loop\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Under-the-Helmet Hood Design</h2>\nUnder-the-helmet hood construction is light and simple\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Sealed-In Warmth</h2>\n\nDrawcord-adjustable drop-tail hem seals in warmth; Fair Trade Certified™ sewn\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Vietnam.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n363 g (12.8 oz)\n</li>\n','\n<li>Shell: 1.4-oz 20-denier 100% recycled polyester with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish</li><li>Lining: 1.3-oz 22-denier 100% recycled polyester with a DWR finish</li><li>Insulation: 60-g PrimaLoft® Gold Insulation Eco 100% polyester (55% postconsumer recycled content)</li><li>Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,249.00,1),(23,'Men\'s Stretch Nano Storm® Jacket','An insulated technical storm shell, built to battle everything from spindrift to sleet. Using a highly breathable liner and FullRange® insulation (now with more recycled content), wrapped in a stretch H2No® Performance Standard shell fabric, the Stretch Nano Storm® keeps you warm, dry and moving. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n\nLight, supple and stretchy 2.5-layer waterproof/breathable H2No® Performance Standard shell fabric made using ECONYL® 100% recycled nylon yarns built from sources that include discarded fishing nets\n</li>\n<li>\nRevolutionary 60-g FullRange® insulation (now 40% recycled) warms and stretches; combined with a highly breathable liner, it allows excess heat to escape\n</li>\n<li>\n\nArticulated pattern and design complement the fabric stretch for enhanced ease of movement; concealed RECCO® reflector\n</li>\n<li>\nAlpine helmet–compatible, two-way-adjustable hood for optimal protection and visibility\n</li>\n<li>\n\nPockets: two welted chest pockets; two welted, high handwarmer pockets, both with DWR (durable water repellent)-treated zippers; two mesh internal catch-all pockets\n</li>\n<li>\nWelted two-way pit zippers help dump heat and are easy to use with gloves\n</li>\n<li>\n\nSelf-fabric hook-and-loop cuff closures and dual-adjust cord-lock system at hem seal out the elements; Fair Trade Certified™ sewn\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Vietnam.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n576 g (20.3 oz)\n</li>\n','\n<li>H2No® Performance Standard shell: 2.5-layer, 2.2-oz 30-denier ECONYL® 100% recycled nylon stretch ripstop with a waterproof/breathable barrier and a DWR (durable water repellent) finish</li><li>Lining: 1.7-oz 100% polyester (87% recycled) plain weave with four-way mechanical stretch and a DWR finish</li><li>Insulation: 60-g FullRange® 100% polyester (40% recycled) stretch</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,399.00,1),(24,'Men\'s R1® TechFace Pullover','A durable, highly technical climbing top with the ideal balance of warmth, breathability and protection. Designed to be abrasion-resistant so it won’t shred against rock, with climbing-specific features like high-stretch cuffs and a deep center-front chest zipper. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n <h2 class=\"h9\">Fleece-Like Comfort with Durable Face Fabric</h2>\nLightweight double-weave fabric is soft and warm next to skin but doesn’t trap heat; face is durable and treated with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish to shed moisture\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Designed for Movement</h2>\n\nStretch fabric and design support a wide range of movement\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Center-Front Zipper</h2>\n\nLow-profile welted center-front zipper helps dump heat\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Zip Chest Pocket</h2>\nExternal zippered left-chest pocket sits behind welt of center-front zipper\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Stuffs Into Chest Pocket</h2>\nSelf-stuffs into chest pocket with carabiner clip-in loop\n</li>\n<li>\n <h2 class=\"h9\">Low-Profile Variable Conditions Cuffs</h2>\nSleek, low-bulk, snag-resistant cuffs with stretch knit push up easily on forearms and provide versatile coverage and comfort\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Fair Trade Sewn</h2>\n\nFair Trade Certified™ sewn\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Vietnam.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n275 g (9.7 oz)\n</li>\n','\n<li>5.2-oz 92% polyester (69% recycled)/8% spandex breathable stretch double weave with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish</li><li>Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,129.00,2),(25,'Men\'s Classic Retro-X® Fleece Vest','A versatile vest made from 100% polyester (50% recycled) sherpa fleece with a bonded windproof membrane to keep your core warm in cool and windy conditions.','\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Wind-Blocking, Heat-Trapping Fleece</h2>\nWindproof membrane bonded between a ¼\"-pile sherpa fleece exterior and a moisture-wicking, highly air-permeable warp-knit mesh\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Center-Front Zipper with Wind Flap</h2>\n\nThe full-length center-front zipper has an internal wind flap for protection\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Pocket Details</h2>\nVertical zippered chest pocket and zippered handwarmer pockets lined with brushed-polyester mesh\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Hip Length</h2>\n\nThe hip length provides additional coverage and pairs well with a hipbelt or harness\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Vietnam.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n507 g (17.9 oz)\n</li>\n','\n<li>Body: 12.9-oz 100% polyester (50% recycled) bonded sherpa fleece</li><li>Lining: 3.2-oz 100% polyester (50% recycled) warp-knit mesh with HeiQ® Fresh durable odor control, a wicking finish and a windproof barrier</li><li>Chest pocket, outer collar and wind flap: 3.4-oz 100% nylon plain weave with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish</li>\n',NULL,149.00,1),(26,'Men\'s Quandary Jacket','A superversatile H2No® Performance Standard waterproof/breathable jacket that stops wind, rain and wet snow. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">H2No® Performance Standard Waterproof/Breathable Shell</h2>\n\n2-layer H2No® Performance Standard waterproof/breathable shell made of 95% nylon (65% recycled) and 5% spandex solid plain weave\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Two-Way-Adjustable Hood</h2>\nThe two-way-adjustable hood provides exceptional coverage and visibility\n</li>\n\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Waterproof Center-Front Zipper</h2>\nThe center-front polyurethane-coated zipper is waterproof and features a zipper garage and a microfleece-lined collar for soft comfort on the skin\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Pocket Details</h2>\nLeft-chest pocket secures with a polyurethane-coated, waterproof zipper; side-entry, zip-closing handwarmer pockets; internal zippered security pocket\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Articulated Sleeves</h2>\n\nArticulated sleeves provide unrestricted movement\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Dual-Adjust Drawcord Hem</h2>\nThe dual-adjust drawcord hem seals out weather and cold air; hip length\n</li>\n\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Supporting the People Who Made This Product</h2>\nFair Trade Certified™ sewn, which means the people who made it earned a premium for their labor\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Vietnam.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n714 g (25.2 oz)\n</li>\n\n','\n<li>H2No® Performance Standard shell: 2-layer, 5.6-oz 95% nylon (65% recycled)/5% spandex solid plain weave</li><li>Lining: 3.8-oz 100% polyester tricot mesh</li><li>Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,199.00,1),(27,'Men\'s Torrentshell 3L Jacket','Simple and unpretentious, our trusted Torrentshell 3L Jacket uses 3-layer H2No® Performance Standard technology for exceptional waterproof/breathable performance, all-day comfort and long-lasting waterproof durability. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">100% Recycled Waterproof/Breathable Face Fabric</h2>\n\n3-layer waterproof/breathable H2No® Performance Standard shell provides the highest levels of comfort and performance, and long-term waterproof durability; Fair Trade Certified™ sewn\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Adjustable Hood</h2>\n\nTwo-way-adjustable hood with a laminated visor rolls down and stows with a simplified cord-and-hook design\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Microfleece-Lined Neck</h2>\nMicrofleece-lined neck provides comfort and protects with a waterproof/breathable barrier\n</li>\n\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Center-Front Zip</h2>\nSnag-free center-front zipper with external and internal storm flaps and zipper-garage chin guard\n</li>\n<li>\n\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Pocket Features</h2>\nTwo zippered handwarmer pockets and venting pit zips; all with welted exterior storm flaps and DWR (durable water repellent)-treated zippers\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Hook-and-Loop Closures</h2>\n\nSelf-fabric hook-and-loop cuff closures and adjustable drawcord hem seal out precipitation\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Self-Stuffs into Hand Pocket</h2>\nJacket self-stuffs into left handwarmer pocket with carabiner clip-in loop\n</li>\n\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Country of Origin</h2>\nMade in Vietnam.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Weight</h2>\n394 g (13.9 oz)\n</li>\n','\n<li>H2No® Performance Standard shell: 3-layer, 3.3-oz 50-denier ECONYL® 100% recycled nylon ripstop face, polycarbonate PU membrane with 13% bio-based content, a tricot backer and a DWR (durable water repellent) finish</li><li>Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved</li><li>Fair Trade Certified™ sewn</li>\n',NULL,149.00,1),(28,'Men\'s Woolyester Fleece Jacket','With heritage design lines, a warm fleece jacket made with a modern fabric blend of recycled wool, polyester and nylon. Fair Trade Certified™ sewn.','\n<li>\n<h2 class=\"h9\">Hard-Working Yet Easy-Wearing