ket is,but how warm it is at the same time.',61,'2020-06-15'),(832,'Joe O.',NULL,'None','S',NULL,5.0,'Down Sweater','Great jacket and fits perfect. Hard to believe something this light can be so warm and comfortable.',61,'2020-06-15'),(833,'Skier 7.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Great down sweater','Received this as a gift. My second one. Love the bright green but the silver is very nice. Fits well,and receive many compliments. Light weight fabric,would not recommend for rough use.',61,'2020-06-15'),(834,'justjoel1',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','XL',NULL,5.0,'Great Gear','I bought this item a little over a month ago. It is now my go to jacket for walking our dogs and very early morning golf . It is very light weigh,but very warm and comfortable. I now own 2 vests and this jacket and looking forward to more purchase in the future.',61,'2020-06-15'),(835,'Local1111',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','XXL',NULL,5.0,'Warm and Great Fit','The Down Sweater was a perfect fit,a warm layer and perfect for all his outings.',61,'2020-06-15'),(836,'Jrova',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','XL',NULL,5.0,'Great jacket','I have other down jackets. I was surprised at how much warmer this Patagonia jacket is versus the other jacket.',61,'2020-06-15'),(837,'Ramp',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','XL',NULL,5.0,'Very nice Jacket','I had the jacket for a few months it sure has worked out well. Light but very warm and a good windbreaker. Easy on and off witch I like.',61,'2020-06-15'),(838,'Mary Z.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Light and Warm!','I bought it for my husband who doesn\'t like heavy jackets. Hands down the most comfortable down jacket he\'s ever worn,per his comments. Roomy enough and good length at the hips. You can layer easily,if you need. Feather grey color was on sale. Super!',61,'2020-06-15'),(839,'Mickey D.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Awesome jacket/sweater','Very comfortable. Packs nice and neat! Keeps the bod warm in a wide range of conditions. If it gets really cold and windy,it works well under a sh