ery happy.',61,'2020-06-15'),(892,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Perfect!','Already had this in blue but bought in black. Wear both all the time. When one is being washed,wear the other.',61,'2020-06-15'),(893,'K C.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','L',NULL,5.0,'Amazing Jacket','What\'s the old saying?... \"Should have... could have...\". That\'s me. I meant to purchase a Down Sweater a few seasons ago,but I didn\'t and I regret my decision. Fear not,I finally bought one and I absolutely love it. I also recently purchased a Nano Puff and I love it as well,but I prefer the Down Sweater as a stand alone s',61,'2020-06-15'),(894,'Mateo V.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,4.0,'Warm and versatile','A little snug in the shoulders but very versatile and warm......best winter jacket I\'ve owned',61,'2020-06-15'),(895,'Beau B.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,4.0,'WARM','So I have this in red and gray. I thought red would be a good color. I also have grey. I have another home in Lake Tahoe and i bought another one of these jackets to leave at my home up there too. Best cold weather jacket!',61,'2020-06-15'),(896,'Caboose',NULL,'5\'1 - 5\'3','S',NULL,5.0,'Its light and very warm','Got this as a Christmas gift,the pattern is grayish and in the sunlight can look green. Its light,it warm and the fits is real; would recommend.',61,'2020-06-15'),(897,'Sarah D.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','S',NULL,5.0,'Comfortably warm!','Bought this for my husband for Christmas. He is in love with it. Great fit,keeps him warm and he\'s able to move around easily in it.',61,'2020-06-15'),(898,'Sagebrush B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','L',NULL,4.0,'Favorite layer!','Worn under my almost antique White Cloud shell,this layer is my go to for most of my ski days. Used 4 out of my five ski days a week!',61,'2020-06-15'),(899,'Christopher J.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,5.0,'Great second jacket (already had the hoodie versio','I bought this as an alt version,since I also purchased the hoodie version. I love both of them,seriou