the standard vest. I like the inside pocket ',44,'2020-06-15'),(1159,'Rick A.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Simple,sustainable and an investment for life.','Bought this last fall,quality of construction and practicality make this a killer vest. I truly expect to have it the rest of my life. Add it traceable down and the sustainability of Patagonia as a company,well its the real deal.',44,'2020-06-15'),(1160,'Aj P.',NULL,'None','S',NULL,5.0,'Snug fit','I bought this vest 2 weeks ago and didn\'t get to wear it until recently because of the unseasonably warm Holiday season. The fit is true and feels extremely light without any restriction to movement. I am thinking of getting the big brother to this line,the hooded jacket,hoping that it shows the same fit and freedom of motion. The only caveat',44,'2020-06-15'),(1161,'Mike C.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','XL',NULL,5.0,'Great midweight insulation','Great midweight down vest. I wear it under lighter shells on times when I need a little extra warmth. I like that it is thin and easily layer-able (if that is a word). Excellent construction. Fits true to size in my opinion',44,'2020-06-15'),(1162,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,4.0,'Warm','I rips to easy is only bad thing. But I have had several and keep coming back for more.....',44,'2020-06-15'),(1163,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','XL',NULL,5.0,'Great product','Very well made,perfect for fall and mild winters,will buy again',44,'2020-06-15'),(1164,'Mark D.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','XXL',NULL,5.0,'Men\'s Down Vest','I bought another one,just because it\'s so handy,versatile,high quality. I love Patagonia products,especially the down.',44,'2020-06-15'),(1165,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Perfect!','Love the sweater vest. A perfect fit and exactly what is needed as fall transitions into winter.',44,'2020-06-15'),(1166,'Minkey',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','S',NULL,5.0,'Great fit,warm,and looks great.','I own the deep blue sea down sweater vest and so far it has been a great addition. It has kept me warm at home whenever I am just lounging or doing things around the house,warm during the current chilly fall commute to and from work or errands,and even at work whenever the occasion allows for wearing the vest where I work.',44,'2020-06-15'),(1167,'Donny C.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Warm and comfortable','A great extra layer and fit. Perfect for everyday use.',44,'2020-06-15'),(1168,'Peter314',NULL,'6\'4 - 6\'6','XXL',NULL,5.0,'My new favorite vest','I have only been wearing this vest for the last week but so far I love it. It\'s lightweight and keeps me warm when the temperature has dropped in the 50\'s. I haven\'t had a chance to test it out in any cooler weather yet.',44,'2020-06-15'),(1169,'Lexingtonva',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'great down vest','I bought as a gift and they loved it!! Would buy again',44,'2020-06-15'),(1170,'Hoon',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'all good in the hood','love my down sweater jacket so it was only natural to add the vest as the weather warms up. also a great layering piece under a snowboard coat or winter hiking.',44,'2020-06-15'),(1171,'Erik R.',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'Perfect Down Vest','So far,so good. I purchased this after researching many competitors\' products. The vest is light,stuffs into an inner pocket,repels water,and keeps me warm while not restricting my movement. I\'ve worn this vest in 20F weather and walked to do errands layered as follows: long-sleeved t-shirt,light fleece 1/4 zip pullover,vest,blue jeans,at',44,'2020-06-15'),(1172,'Dksf',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'Had this for years, wear it every day','Had mine for years. Keep it right next the door along with my house keys. Wear it every day that ends in a y. Walking the dog? Check. Going to get coffee? Check. Headed out for dawn patrol and the fog is an inch thick? check. Headed to the crag? Check. Great for bay area where you can pair it with a tshirt and sunglasses, or a thick wool sweater an',44,'2020-06-15'),(1173,'Jkln',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'Works great everywhere','I have purchased three of these vests for my family and they wear them everywhere. It\'s warm enough to wear by itself or can be used as an added layer when needed. It\'s been used skating, skiing, fishing, hanging out at the lake, and even as a layer snowmobiling. I would like to see more colors so I can order more.',44,'2020-06-15'),(1174,'Beau B.',NULL,'None','None',NULL,1.0,'Disappointed','This is a great vest with one exception, the zipper closure at the neck. The zipper guard creates a stiff section of the collar that digs into your chin and neck. The collar isn\'t rounded all the way around the neck, maybe three quarters of the way and then it\'s squared off in the spot you expect it to be round. This does not break in wit',44,'2020-06-15'),(1175,'Edu1',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'Awesome vest','It is exactly what I was looking for. Simple and efficient. I got an M size.',44,'2020-06-15'),(1176,'Porsche',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'Best stuff on earth','Can\'t live without it. I am so used to wear my vest to keep me warm and organize everyday with all the right pockets. My Patagonia vest Not only gave me everyday comfort also gave me style and a brand respected worldwide',44,'2020-06-15'),(1177,'Matt F.',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'Big warmth in small package','This down vest packs so small and when combined with a couple under layers is the perfect traveling jacket for climates that are cold but not wet. Just wore in the high desert Arizona and worked great.',44,'2020-06-15'),(1178,'Davidtothemoon',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'Light and toasty','Super styley, and warm and light. Digging my down vest for colder days on the mountain, absolutely, but mostly digging it around town and traveling. Nothing\'s cozier than down.',44,'2020-06-15'),(1179,'Satisfied',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'Warm and fits great','I\'m very happy with the flexibility this vest offers - I\'m able to wear it under a 