rother loves this vest. It fits well and goes with everything.',17,'2020-06-15'),(1368,'Nina L.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Nina','My husband loves this vest! It\'s perfect, not a huge commitment meaning it\'s not thick and bulky, yet gives you that extra bit of warmth on chilly winter days. Whether you\'re inside or outside, it\'s another layer to keep you warm. It\'s a great quality, as can be expected of Patagonia. I\'m ordering another one tonight i',17,'2020-06-15'),(1369,'Jade',NULL,'None','L',NULL,1.0,'Picture is not accurate','The nickel color looks nothing like the picture. It’s a flat, dark grey not a lighter, heathered grey like the picture.',17,'2020-06-15'),(1370,'Jeff',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','XL',NULL,1.0,'Not so proud owner of two of these vests :-(','Recently purchased. a dark blue and black Synchilla vest. While they are warm and comfortable, the vests sheds incredibly bad. We\'ve machine washed them and still no reduction in the amount of material coming off and sticking to other garments. While outdoors on the weekends no big deal but I like to wear these to work since our office is cool',17,'2020-06-15'),(1371,'Dylan',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Favorite Jacket','By far my new favorite jacket. Super comfy, stylish, looks great. I\'m military and stationed out in Hawaii for only a few more months, and it got shipped here super quick. I couldn\'t believe it only took a week. I cant wait to be able to wear it everyday, it can totally be used as a ski or snowboarding jacket. Lots of pockets. Fits true t',43,'2020-06-15'),(1372,'Daniel',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','S',NULL,5.0,'Convenient','This jacket has been phenomenal. I live in the PNW and it is built for just that. Not to mention the impeccable customer service provided by Patagonia. Keep up the great work!',43,'2020-06-15'),(1373,'Mikolaj W.',NULL,'None','M',NULL,3.0,'The Old Tres Was Better','Some stylistic changes to this classic that I was not a fan of, I ended up returning it and upgrading