duct','this vest does exactly what it is supposed to do - it\'s warm and windproof, but not bulky at all, so it can either we worn inside or outside other layers. great for traveling due to its packability.',18,'2020-06-15'),(1747,'Anthony M.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Very warm, might want to size up','For all shirts and coats, if I want a good fit then I get a small or even possibly an extra small. I was about to order a small, but I tried this on in Nordstrom and realized a medium would actually be a little snug but the good type of snug. It is warm for a vest and works good in all those aspects, but I recommend trying it on beforehand in case ',18,'2020-06-15'),(1748,'Jason D.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','S',NULL,5.0,'Great product!','I’ve owned this nano puff vest for almost 2 years. It is an essential piece of my winter gear. Light weight, stuffable into a bag, and allows for more mobility than wearing a jacket. Keeps my core warm and blocks wind very well.',18,'2020-06-15'),(1749,'Bodie H.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','M',NULL,5.0,'Love this Vest so much i have 2 and want a 3rd','Living in Arizona this vest is perfect for everything, fits great, extremely durrable, looks great, and the primaloft has the perfect balance of warmth and wind blocker for all my adventures in the city or the mountains. Im 6\'2 and have 32\" waist so i wear a Medium and it fits perfect!',18,'2020-06-15'),(1750,'Nm S.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','M',NULL,5.0,'Best Vest','Great vest for any activity. Have black and gray, wish they had the classic navy like the jacket.',18,'2020-06-15'),(1751,'Bobcat',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','XL',NULL,4.0,'Overall Good But,','Tiny bit too long so that it rides up when I sit down and the armholes are too small if you plan to wear anything under it.',18,'2020-06-15'),(1752,'Lechle3',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,4.0,'Great vest while it lasted','I got this vest as a gift last year and absolutely loved it! The fit is true to size,it\'s warm,light,packs really well and is super 