ind well. Warm down','Blocks wind well. Warm down to mid twenties. Slim fit and very versatile.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1930,'Beau B.',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'Grandson said it’s perfect!','Grandson said it’s perfect!',22,'2020-06-15'),(1931,'Kenneth G.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,4.0,'First, the disappointments: it\'s not','First, the disappointments: it\'s not as warm as I had expected and it\'s very tight around my (ahem) mature butt. That said, the hood is gently elasticized and so is snug and reasonable warm even in breeze. The jacket is water resistant - it kept moisture out during a downpour. It is well designed with a collar that seals well, zips for th',22,'2020-06-15'),(1932,'Lori',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','XL',NULL,4.0,'Works as advertised; a little','Works as advertised; a little tight around the waist, but otherwise great',22,'2020-06-15'),(1933,'Sudarshan N.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,4.0,'Really warm','This jacket is great for cold and windy days, and the hood works to keep wind out of your neck and ears. It fit a little large on me',22,'2020-06-15'),(1934,'Neal E.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','M',NULL,5.0,'Go to cool weather jacket','This is my second nano puff. This jacket travels with me almost all year, offering cold weather warmth, wind protection and breathable enough for cool mornings and evening. Also great on planes. The trim fit encourages layering, and the hood is fits well without draw strings.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1935,'Beau B.',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'Amazing','Amazing',22,'2020-06-15'),(1936,'Garrett F.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','S',NULL,5.0,'Hoody','Very warm and stylish',22,'2020-06-15'),(1937,'KOICHI I.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','S',NULL,5.0,'Very light and super warm','I walked around city streets when it was below 32. No longer need a heavy winter coat. The hood was a big plus. It runs large and replaced M with S which fits me perfectly (5”11).',22,'2020-06-15'),(1938,'Ralph S.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Great item! Size is slightly','Great item!