y, bulky winter jacket!',22,'2020-06-15'),(1965,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','S/M',NULL,5.0,'Best jacket I’ve owned!','Best jacket I’ve owned!',22,'2020-06-15'),(1966,'Michael M.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Absolutely love it!','My fiancé is on her second nano puff, and she’s been raving about it for years. I finally saw one on sale and got mine. It’s my every day jacket now in the Pacific Northwest winter.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1967,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Great jacket','Well made! Coupled with Cloud ridge jacket to cut the wind, this jacket works great to retain warmth. Zippers and seams all seem strong. Gonna rock this jacket till it crawls off of me lol!',22,'2020-06-15'),(1968,'John G.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','XXL',NULL,5.0,'Wow','I\'ve waited 2 years to buy this jacket. I wish that I hadn\'t. Its light weight but fantastically warm. I told my wife that if soft chocolate chip cookies were a jacket, they would be this jacket. You can wear a tee shirt and this coat in the cold and you are completely warm. It looks awesome too.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1969,'Steve T.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','L',NULL,5.0,'Had buyer\'s remorse until I received jacket.','I found this jacket for $100 off and decided to give it a shot. It\'s super light, but feels like wearing a warm blanket. I love it!',22,'2020-06-15'),(1970,'Ronald M.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','XXL',NULL,5.0,'Nano Puffs Rule!','This is my fifth Nano Puff. I wanted to get one with a hood, hence this addition. Nano Puff\'s cool colors, a fit that\'s perfect for me and it\'s light weight make it the perfect coat for me. Sure glad I got it!',22,'2020-06-15'),(1971,'Caleb C.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','NB-7lb',NULL,5.0,'The Most Delightful Synthetic Joey Pouch Ever Made!!!','I bought this jacket because I am a college student who must make a brisk quest to his classes each morning across an entire college campus. I am a huge fan of Patagonia products in general because they are deluxe quality and environmentally aware. So I decided to nab this Nano Puff Hoodie Jacket. I had high expectations that were beyond exploded b',22,'2020-06-15'),(1972,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','XL',NULL,5.0,'Great Jacket','This is the second patagonia nano puff jacket I have purchased and you can not beat the weight to warmth ration.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1973,'Jeffrey R.',NULL,'6\'4 - 6\'6','M/L',NULL,5.0,'A perfect gift for hubby','My hubby is always feeling cold outside, so I got this jacket and he said it works very well and he loves it.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1974,'Claire P.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Nano puff hoody','Love my nano puff hoody. Just right for most of the winter weather in Texas.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1975,'Steve T.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'The EDC Jacket','The men’s nano puff has proven to be the every day carry jacket. No matter where I’m going, whether it be in to the city or into the mountains, I always take a nano puff. The versatile jacket works in a wide range of temperatures to keep you warm and cozy. Use it alone or layer up under your favorite hard-shell. Highly recommend this jacket.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1976,'Scott M.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','NB-7lb',NULL,5.0,'Quality & Performance','Well made using high quality materials and techniques that lessen the environmental impact of production and distribution. True to size. Very lightweight and super warm. Complete freedom of movement.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1977,'Josh E.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,4.0,'Nice light jacket','This seems like a nice light jacket, but I returned it for the Macro puff jacket.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1978,'Erik H.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,5.0,'Much more my speed','I originally purchased the Micro puff, and although it was a nice jacket it was just two light and not as warm as I wanted/needed. The feature were not what I needed (pack ability, lightweight, etc.) Plus it was just too thin for my liking. This Nano is perfect. Much warmer but I still wouldn\'t take this jacket on a stroll under 30 deg. It is',22,'2020-06-15'),(1979,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'I’m 6 ft so I','I’m 6 ft so I could have went with a medium but I’m enjoying it!',22,'2020-06-15'),(1980,'Derek N.',NULL,'5\'1 - 5\'3','M',NULL,5.0,'Wow!!!','I wish I found sooner! I work in temps as low as -30 degrees and I use this as a mid layer. This stops the wind completely! I have bought this for work only but plan to get one that is more fitting so I can have it as a good coat for the days I\'m off! Love it.. and SO many people have asked about it and I only have good things to say. Worth ev',22,'2020-06-15'),(1981,'Tobias C.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Great hooded jacket so far','I’ve only worn it a couple times, but it fits great and everything seems to be in the right place.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1982,'A g.',NULL,'None','L',NULL,5.0,'Nano Puff Hoody','Outstanding warmth to weight ratio and great colors to choose from . The cut is perfect for outdoor activities with room in all the right places .',22,'2020-06-15'),(1983,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Excellent','Excellent',22,'2020-06-15'),(1984,'Michael W.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','M',NULL,5.0,'Nice addition to any outdoor','Nice addition to any outdoor activities',22,'2020-06-15'),(1985,'Beau B.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','M',NULL,5.0,'Great jacket','Warm and comfy jacket. Fit is a little large for a medium. I’m 6’1” and I’ll have to have the sleeves shortened. Always buy a medium from them with no issues historically.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1986,'Ron A.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','S',NULL,5.0,'I love the Nano Puff','I love the Nano Puff it is the perfect jacket for those chilly days at the crag.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1987,'Ridley',NULL,'None','M',NULL,4.0,'Almost Perfect','As other reviews have mentioned, if you\'re in the 5\'10\" / 34\" waist neighborhood with an athletic build, Patagonia really doesn\'t have a size for you. This jacket is too tight in the chest and makes the hood almost unusable. At the same time the body of the jacket fits well while the sleeves are almost too long. A size up w',22,'2020-06-15'),(1988,'Rachel D.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','S',NULL,5.0,'Great product!','Very lightweight and warm!',22,'2020-06-15'),(1989,'Christian B.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','S',NULL,4.0,'It\'s really good! Everything was','It\'s really good! Everything was definitely thought through with this product as it\'s very comfortable, warm, light, and versatile. My only problem with it is the arm sleeves are a tad bit too long.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1990,'John P.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Wow','I absolutely LOVE this jacket. I seem to wear it all the time now. Versatile in such a range of weather. Love, love, love, and super comfy!',22,'2020-06-15'),(1991,'Kim R.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'another awesome item','great Hoody, light, fluffy, warm! I love the hood, wouldn\'t want one without.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1992,'Ben A.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','XL',NULL,5.0,'Best Jacket of All Time','Such a great jacket. For casual, dress, or travel, it’s the best.',22,'2020-06-15'),(1993,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'It’s everything I wanted','Water resistant, dries super fast, warm when wet, light, packs small, what’s not to like??',22,'2020-06-15'),(1994,'Jacob J.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','XL',NULL,5.0,'Excellent fitting garment','Excellent fitting garment',22,'2020-06-15'),(1995,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Love it','This is my son’s second one and he lives in it! Not too big, just perfect for fall in Ohio',22,'2020-06-15'),(1996,'Ammi R.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','XL',NULL,5.0,'Finally one of my own','I have been borrowing my husband’s Nano Puff Hoody for years. Got so disappointed when he himself were using it. But now I got my own and I enjoy it fully! Such a great jacket!',22,'2020-06-15'),(1997,'John B.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','XL',NULL,5.0,'The nano puff hoody has','The nano puff hoody has a lot of warmth for its weight and the hoody is great for when you want even more warmth. Plus I like how you can stuf