acket has a thin liner which adds some extra warmth and wind resistance. I really like the vintage track jacket look at feel. This jacket can be dressed up for going out or worn down with shorts. If you\'re looking for a daily-wear jacket,this is it. I',33,'2020-06-15'),(2593,'Ray',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Great item','This is my 2nd purchase My other jackey is 10 years old. I just bought a black and blue to replace it!',56,'2020-06-15'),(2594,'Stephen',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','0',NULL,1.0,'Shedding','Material sheds an incredible amount, I love Patagonia products but this seems unacceptable. You can literally put your hand through the fabric and pull away a ton of \"fuzz\". Wore on a business trip and had an embarrassing amount of shedding on my dress shirt. Received as a gift for Christmas, put through the wash/dryer a couple of times h',56,'2020-06-15'),(2595,'Sean G.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','XL',NULL,5.0,'Great sweater for my dad','Great sweater for my dad :)',56,'2020-06-15'),(2596,'Jeffrey B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Size design','For my 5-11 frame, a medium size is just right for my arms length. However, could use a large to wear other thicker shirts. The sleeves on the large are way too long. Will use and wear thin type shirts instead.',56,'2020-06-15'),(2597,'Suzanne M.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','XL',NULL,5.0,'So soft','Gift for my husband and he loved it. Warm but not too warm and also not too light. The oatmeal color is great. Well made and size is true. Highly recommend.',56,'2020-06-15'),(2598,'Gerry L.',NULL,'6\'4 - 6\'6','L',NULL,5.0,'Men\'s Classic Synchilla Jacket, Navy','My husband loves these jackets. They are warm, fit very well and look good on. The full length zipper is a favorite, too.',56,'2020-06-15'),(2599,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Loved it!','Christmas gift for hubby and he loves it and looks great in it. I want one!',56,'2020-06-15'),(2600,'Beau B.',NULL,'None','XL',NULL,5.0,'Love everything about this jacket!','Love e