s',45,'2020-06-15'),(3343,'Beau B.',NULL,'6\'4 - 6\'6','XXL',NULL,4.0,'2018-19 last year’s model','Quite happy I was still able to purchase last year’s model. They have changed It up this year and made the better sweater very tight in the sleeves. Impossible to wear over layers.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3344,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Great sweater','Usually would not spend this much money on a sweater jacket, but the warmth, quality, look, and fit are just perfect. I got the large and I am a little over 5’11 and weigh 210 lbs.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3345,'Ronald C.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Very comfy.','Very comfy.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3346,'Suzanne P.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Better sweater jacket','The large was too roomy so it was returned for a medium. There seems to be too much difference between the M and the L, and I wish you made a M+ size. But for now the M works (almost) perfectly fine. As always, thank you for your outstanding service and great quality.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3347,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Best sweater!','Love this sweater! Perfect fit, very warm and good looking!',45,'2020-06-15'),(3348,'Lisa K.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','L',NULL,5.0,'Puurfect','My 2nd color and very pleased.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3349,'Scott M.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Surprised comfort and warmth','I buy a lot of TNF and This was my first Patagonia purchase. My sons (19, 21) told me my jacket was cool. That was a first. The sweater jacket is very warm without bulk. The quality of the workmanship is a bit more (IMO) than TNF. The sleeves are snug. Compared to my other jackets but not to the annoying point. Would I buy this again and would I re',45,'2020-06-15'),(3350,'BR',NULL,'None','XS',NULL,4.0,'Comfy, cozy, but too big','I purchased this item in the same size as the Better Sweater 1/4 zip in an XS. I got this delivered recently, and it\'s much, much larger and doesn\'t fit as well as the 1/4 zip that I have in the same size. I had to return it as there isn\'t a size smaller than XS. :(',45,'2020-06-15'),(3351,'Colleen H.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,5.0,'Great sweater jacket. We love','Great sweater jacket. We love Patagonia !',45,'2020-06-15'),(3352,'Brenda F.',NULL,'5\'0 or less','L',NULL,5.0,'Nice','Nice',45,'2020-06-15'),(3353,'shaun m.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','M',NULL,5.0,'Great sweater','I have been meaning to buy this sweater for a while now so glad I did I use it every day for work and it’s holding up well in the ruff conditions very happy and warm',45,'2020-06-15'),(3354,'Steven W.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','S',NULL,2.0,'Best bet for the tropics','This is a beautiful looking - and fitting - piece of gear which has almost no insulating value whatsoever. It’s not just that it’s porous to the wind, like many pile garments - it’s just not warm. Someone else compared its warmth to that of a flannel shirt. I would say that would be a pretty skimpy flannel shirt. Too bad, because the design is grea',45,'2020-06-15'),(3355,'Rob T.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Best sweater jacket','Love the better sweater full zip. Warm, moves with you and is not too bulky. Cleaner drape than the R2’s although I am a huge fan of the R2 as well, the Better sweater is more of a sweater than a jacket, which I guess is precisely the point!',45,'2020-06-15'),(3356,'Matthew K.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Good for casual wear','Got this jacket for casual wear, not for serious outdoor pursuits. Understated style works well for that purpose because it doesn\'t look as teched out as some other fleece jackets.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3357,'Kevin C.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','S',NULL,5.0,'Great fleece','Can’t go wrong with better sweaters. They’ve been proven. Sleeves are a bit slimmer in this model than some of my other Patagonia gear like the quilted snap sweater.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3358,'Matthew F.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Great for fall weather','Great color and great functionality. This sweater is very warm and i