ugh for everyday. I would wear it all of the time and it is holding up great.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3447,'Mikef',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Love this sweater','I had coveted this sweater since seeing it on a friend earlier in the year and finally got around to buying it when I saw a deal. I\'ve been buying outdoor gear for a very long time and have found a couple of items that what I would consider near-perfect. One is the Buff and now I\'m adding this one to that list. I love this thing. It ain&#',45,'2020-06-15'),(3448,'Marc',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,2.0,'Needs to be cleaned up','Excessive material under the arm and by the chest Sloppy-looking Needs to be cleaned up',45,'2020-06-15'),(3449,'tbone1523',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,2.0,'Sizing off','I purchased my first better sweater 5 or 6 years ago in a medium. It is certainly one of my favorite pieces for everyday use in the winter. I recently purchased another one,also in a medium.. The \"new\" medium,to my dislike,is definitely longer in the sleeves and waist. Unfortunately I took off the tags and threw it straight in the wash wh',45,'2020-06-15'),(3450,'Lc2017',NULL,'None','L',NULL,2.0,'so much pilling','I bought this as a gift for my boyfriend\'s birthday. He\'s had it less than a month and there is already significant pilling all over the jacket. He only uses it for casual wear to work. I expected higher quality given the brand and the price.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3451,'Gmb11',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,2.0,'Warm and comfortable but quality questionable','I really enjoy the comfort and warmth that the Better Sweater provides but I question the quality. The pilling on this product is disappointing. I would also recommend Patagonia put some type of protective material on the collar so that those of us with a beard don\'t destroy it. Still a huge fan of Patagonia,please renew your focus on the smal',45,'2020-06-15'),(3452,'Ann S.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','M',NULL,2.0,'Jacket','Good looking jacket but wind cuts right through it',45,'2020-06-15'),(3453,'Beau B.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','XL',NULL,5.0,'Most favorite thing ever!','That was my brother in laws response. He wears it all the time and basically only takes it off to wash it. We live in Minnesota and he works outdoors and this sweater keeps you so warm. He hasn\'t purchased a single sweatshirt since we gifted him the Patagonia Better Sweater. He didn\'t think he needed any \'fancy\' things but as he',45,'2020-06-15'),(3454,'Guennadisereda',NULL,'6\'4 - 6\'6','XL',NULL,5.0,'Great,verstatile sweater','Believe the hype,this is a perfect example of patagonia quality.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3455,'Felipe P.',NULL,'None','S',NULL,4.0,'Nice for the price','I bought this one thinking it was the same product than one I tried in one of the REI stores. Only different color. I did not feel the same and did not fit the same with the one I tried in the store. Although,it is pretty nice and I like it a lot now.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3456,'Mike L.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,3.0,'Decline in quality','This is my second better sweater jacket and it appears that the materials that are currently being used are of a lesser quality than those of previous years. It\'s the small touches,such as cheaper zippers and a decrease in the thickness of the fleece. I\'m still fairly happy with it,but wish they had maintained the level of quality they pr',45,'2020-06-15'),(3457,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','XL',NULL,5.0,'Great jacket','Great jacket. Fits very well,More room than the performance better sweater. Also bought regular performance better sweater in same color - very different,both for different outfits/activities. I am 6ft,220 and the XL was prefect in both styles.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3458,'Phome',NULL,'None','S',NULL,5.0,'Great fleece','Fits great! I\'ve got a hooded and regular version. Love both!',45,'2020-06-15'),(3459,'brianmj',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Very Warm and comfortable','Had this sweater a couple months now and i am completely satisfied. It is the comfiest sweater ive ever had hands down. Highly reccommend.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3460,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Fits Great!','I was worried the fit would be a little tight just by looking at the shape of the jacket,but it actually fits nicely and has a nice amount of snugness to it. It\'s great for casually wearing in not too cold temperatures and it actually does well in the wind too!',45,'2020-06-15'),(3461,'Bulk12',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'The names says it all.','I live in these sweaters,so comfortable. I love the simple,clean look.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3462,'Karl R.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Comfortable jacket','Very comfortable jacket,runs a little to the large size.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3463,'dink1',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','L',NULL,1.0,'Better sweater jacket: Did not fit well and','I first bought a M size but realizing it was too tight,decided to exchange it for an L size. The exchange went very smooth,but the problem is that I\'m between sizes,and upon wearing the L size once (for less than 1hr on a cold day),I realized that it would not work out either. I called for an exchange for another item,but was told that since I',45,'2020-06-15'),(3464,'Beau B.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,5.0,'A favorite jacket!','My husband loves these sweater/jackets and now has 5 in various colors. The fit is true and the mediterrean blue color is perfect for spring.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3465,'David',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','XL',NULL,3.0,'Nice looking but provides no warmth.','I\'m probably being harsh as I live in an area still experiencing snowfall in early April but I purchased this as it looked nice. It arrived,fit well and looks nice; however,it provides no more warmth than a flannel shirt. A good sweater for high 50s at best.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3466,'Armchair',NULL,'6\'4 - 6\'6','L',NULL,5.0,'I didn\'t want it,I needed it.','Wear it as my staple layer. All year long and all year comfort. Looks incredible and construction is flawless.