ter Sweater is so comfortable and warm. It\'s also a great looking piece to wear as a mid layer or just around town. My wife just bought one for herself as she loves it!',45,'2020-06-15'),(3495,'Oldguy77',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','XXL',NULL,5.0,'Pricey but really well made','I wouldn\'t have spent the money for this sweater jacket ,being very conservative by nature,but my wonderful daughter-in-law gave it to me for Christmas,and,what a present. I wear it every day. Easy to put on and take off. Really warm. Well made.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3496,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Perfect !','Perfect jacket! Warm and comfortable! Will buy again. Thank you !',45,'2020-06-15'),(3497,'R847',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,3.0,'Sleeves long','5\'10 150,sleeves about 2 inches long,small fits too tight',45,'2020-06-15'),(3498,'Jesse A.',NULL,'None','L',NULL,5.0,'Quality fleece','Good quality fleece,gets the job done. Held up nice so far',45,'2020-06-15'),(3499,'Steve',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Super styled and very warm','Bought this after looking at similar fleece garments.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3500,'Beau B.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,5.0,'Very Comfy!','This is my third color and size of this jacket... as my son has grown this is one of his favorite items. He would rather wear this than a sweatshirt.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3501,'Beau B.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','M',NULL,5.0,'Great gift for boyfriend!','I bought this for my boyfriend for Christmas,and he loves it! He wears it all of the time,its the perfect weight if you don\'t live somewhere too cold (we\'re in Arizona).',45,'2020-06-15'),(3502,'Jjm3610',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','S',NULL,4.0,'Extreme pilling occuring','I love these better sweaters!! I have four of them,including one that I bought back in 2009 and it is still going strong. However,one of them,which I haven\'t washed too many times,has started to pill up something fierce. I\'m not washing it in any different way from my others,but it\'s getting to the point where it\'s 