's a little longer so it doesn\'t lift up when active.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3519,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Good quality!','The jacket runs true to size and is nice quality. I ordered the Pale Khaki color and it looks good.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3520,'Gingerbread',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','XL',NULL,5.0,'Runs slim','This would have been great if my husband wasn\'t so portly! Nice jacket,just way too small. I took it back.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3521,'Bullboy',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Warm,comfortable fabric','I have worn this jacket in 15 degree temps and has kept me warm. I ordered the stone color which is a nice neutral shade.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3522,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','L',NULL,5.0,'Well made!','Will buy a second one. This product should be made in the USA.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3523,'Nathan W.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,4.0,'Super','My wife bought one,then I bought one,then my 4 kids got one and now my extended family has them. The only negative (for some) is that the sleeves run a bit longer than usual for all of us. Some like that,some don\'t. Overall we all love the Better Sweater.',45,'2020-06-15'),(3524,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Well made!','Love the better sweater',45,'2020-06-15'),(3525,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','L',NULL,5.0,'Great Jacket!','I bought this for my dad as a Christmas gift in addition to buying him the Men\'s Better Vest which he already owns and loves. This jacket did not disappoint! My dad is a fisherman,a contractor and a business owner so he\'s up and out early most cold mornings while most people are still in bed so he needed something warm and functional and',45,'2020-06-15'),(3526,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Best jacket I own!','Absolutely amazing product. Fits very well,the color is great,and it is very warm!',45,'2020-06-15'),(3527,'Keith F.',NULL,'None','M',NULL,5.0,'Warm,comfortable and looks great','This jacket is warm and comfortable. It\'s perfect for a hike or being out and 