cket!',68,'2020-06-15'),(3790,'John E.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Retro-X Jacket','Love the fit and color',68,'2020-06-15'),(3791,'Bruno L.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Retro-X','Love the Retro-X, I’ve been wearing Patagonia gear for over 20 years and am always impressed by the workmanship, quality and longevity of their products. This recently purchased Retro-X jacket does not disappoint. Patagonia is the best!!',68,'2020-06-15'),(3792,'Mindro H.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'My great quality','My husband loves it! Cool casual design makes 58 yr old guy looks younger!',68,'2020-06-15'),(3793,'Dain K.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','M',NULL,4.0,'Cute oversized fleece jacket','I\'m a 5\'4 girl (normally size small) but ordered the men\'s retro x jacket in medium for a more boxy, oversized fit. Fits perfectly oversized in the body, but the arms are way too long. I have other men\'s medium sized clothes and the arms are usually not THIS long... I wish Patagonia offered alteration services because I would lo',68,'2020-06-15'),(3794,'youngbae L.',NULL,'5\'0 or less','L',NULL,5.0,'Too good.','Warm. The fit I wanted.',68,'2020-06-15'),(3795,'Colin D.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,4.0,'Great Winter Jacket','This jacket is great for the winter! Worn it almost every day since I got it, and it\'s kept me warm and comfortable. Easy to layer underneath, but also comfortable enough to just wear a t shirt underneath and be perfectly warm in normal winter conditions.',68,'2020-06-15'),(3796,'Benjamin',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','XXL',NULL,5.0,'Wonderful Fleece Jacket','Haven\'t had this for very long, but so far it\'s a wonderful fleece jacket (Pelican w/ Wren Gold). I\'ve already gotten several admiring comments on it. The jacket is beautifully made and is pretty true to size. If you\'re expecting a cuddly, soft fleece jacket - this truthfully isn\'t really it. While the Sherpa fleece outer l',68,'2020-06-15'),(3797,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Retro-X rocks!','After