bows.',68,'2020-06-15'),(3835,'Golfwheels',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,4.0,'Solid jacket','I wanted to love this jacket but ran into the same problem many other reviewers encountered...I\'m 6\'2\' tall 200 lbs and have difficulty finding clothes that fit tall slim without looking like a circus tent. Fortunately most L Patagonia tops fit perfectly (thanks to patagonia for staying true to its clients) but this jacket was the ex',68,'2020-06-15'),(3836,'Tommy D.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Awesome Coat','I am so Happy with my Retro Fleece Coat it took a long time to get so I am happy now,I wanted Feather Grey but settled for Black and charcoal :-)',68,'2020-06-15'),(3837,'James H.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'My favorite Patagonia Jacket','This jacket is the real deal. If you are looking for a reliable,fashionable jacket that will keep you more than warm in below freezing temperatures this is the jacket for you. They used to make these jackets wider in the torso to use as a over coat but with their newest model it is a bit slimmer then it used to be making it good comfortable fit for',68,'2020-06-15'),(3838,'Jason',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','XL',NULL,5.0,'Just what I needed','This is the perfect jacket when you need to layer up,when it\'s super cold',68,'2020-06-15'),(3839,'PMSchram',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','XL',NULL,4.0,'Warm and Wind Resistant','I bought this from the web site in an XL,it was too big for me so back to Patagonia it went. Patagonia didn\'t have the jacket in my size so I bought it from another outdoor company in a large and I love it.',68,'2020-06-15'),(3840,'Greek',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','XL',NULL,2.0,'what\'s going on?','I love my retro fleece XL i bought 1 year ago and when they went on sale I said let\'sa \"get another one\". This one is much different. smaller,the pockets are a bit higher. I just seems smaller than an XL as I have known Patagonia for my whole life.',68,'2020-06-15'),(3841,'Sean M.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Great Warmth','Thi