.',100,'2020-06-15'),(4354,'Katie W.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,3.0,'Very very thin. Not a coat.','This is a good looking and well made shirt. My son likes it and the L fits him well. He’s 6’1” and has trouble with sleeve length, but this was adequate. I’m just not impressed with the fabric and I fear it will be very easily torn and or worn. Time will tell.',100,'2020-06-15'),(4355,'Scott C.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','S',NULL,5.0,'Excellent','Warm, lightweight, bit of stretch, fits well, and it looks fantastic. The tag has no washing info, but just hand wash in cold water and air dry. Love this thing.',100,'2020-06-15'),(4356,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Exactly what was advertised!','Perfect for the current weather, easily fits on top of a long sleeve shirt. Looks great too.',100,'2020-06-15'),(4357,'JJ',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'soft, lightweight, and warm','Given this jacket as a gift and here is the feedback from the recipient: lightweight and warm. The material is soft and not itchy at all. Also there are lots of great details - hidden pocket, lining, etc.',100,'2020-06-15'),(4358,'Chase K.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,5.0,'Comfortable and Practical','It fits well and it very comfortable. I like the different material around the edges of the coat and it looks like it will last a long time.',100,'2020-06-15'),(4359,'Theodore W.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','S',NULL,5.0,'Woolie Coat Works','I have a very similar old school all wool sweater (kind of frumpy in a Mr. Rogers kind of way) that I simply love. This version brings the concept into modern times. The size is as advertised and the colour is traditional, which fits the concept of the garment. My overall satisfaction aside, I do have two small personal peccadillos to comment on: 1',100,'2020-06-15'),(4360,'Gregory C.',NULL,'None','M',NULL,5.0,'Excellent Product','A classic looking fleece. Super warm, very casual style. Reminds me of synchilla but a little more coarse. Size runs large.',100,'2020-06-15'),(4