nia. I am very happy with how light it feels while wearing and yet how much warmth it provides too. I am very happy with my purchase, plan on ordering a couple more in different colors.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4370,'Jun W.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Soft and balanced warm','Its great to wear for cool weather and you wont overheat. A simple jacket on top for colder weathers will suffice. And its stylish',109,'2020-06-15'),(4371,'Joanne D.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','XXL',NULL,5.0,'Beautiful lightweight casual Pullover','Gave this beautiful navy pullover to my son-in-law and he loved it! He usually runs warm and seldom needs a coat or heavy sweatshirt or sweater. This pullover is warm, but is very lightweight, so he loves it. Would definitely recommend it for the type who needs coverage from the cold, but tends to get too warm when in the car or when wearing heavie',109,'2020-06-15'),(4372,'David B.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','M',NULL,5.0,'Fair','Good quality. Good to use it around Los Angeles type of weather',109,'2020-06-15'),(4373,'Jerry S.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','M',NULL,5.0,'Have eight. Can\'t get enough.','Have eight. Can\'t get enough. Soft, comfortable and perfect fit.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4374,'Kim K.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'My son loved the fit','My son loved the fit and comfort.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4375,'L J.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','M',NULL,5.0,'Gift well received','Gave this to my brother-in-law, fit well, well made and well received.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4376,'Willette O.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Satisfied customer','This was a Christmas gift for my son and he loved it!',109,'2020-06-15'),(4377,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','LM',NULL,5.0,'It’s all good.','It’s all good.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4378,'Jason K.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','M',NULL,5.0,'Awesome','Yeah!',109,'2020-06-15'),(4379,'dreme n.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','S',NULL,5.0,'Easy and smooth transaction and','Easy and smooth transaction and fast shipping.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4380,'Rick M.',NULL,'None','XXL',N