at product!!','Delivered on time as promised.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4399,'Melissa B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','L',NULL,5.0,'Lightweight and warm','I ordered 2 of the new Micro D shirts for myself and my husband. My hubby\'s was slightly small on him (Large). So I kept his too and ordered him a new one in XL bc if his burly upper body. I got lucky this holiday with 2 new awesome Micro Ds.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4400,'Susan K.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','M/L',NULL,5.0,'Love it','Love it',109,'2020-06-15'),(4401,'Jon W.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L/XL',NULL,5.0,'Great buy/ nice fit /','Great buy/ nice fit / looks great',109,'2020-06-15'),(4402,'Faye H.',NULL,'5\'4- 5\'6','XS',NULL,5.0,'Good quality and nice fit,','Good quality and nice fit, color looks the same in person.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4403,'Rose T.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','NB-7lb',NULL,5.0,'Micro D navy blue pullover','My grandson loved it. Very soft and size was true.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4404,'Beau B.',NULL,'None','None',NULL,5.0,'Men’s micro pullover','Fast delivery and great product.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4405,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'7 - 5\'9','XL',NULL,5.0,'Ms Micro D® Pullover','Very nice product. Soft and warm for a mid-weight garment. True to size. Works great as a under layer when it is really cold outside and as an outer layer when engaging in physical activity, i.e. biking and hiking.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4406,'Meghan C.',NULL,'6\'1 - 6\'3','L',NULL,5.0,'Amazing Gift','This is a gift so unfortunately I cannot upload pictures because the elves already wrapped it!!! So soft! And the color selection is EARTHY and woodsy for my cabin-lover companion! Great purchase especially for the price!',109,'2020-06-15'),(4407,'Mark G.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Lighter weight than expected for','Lighter weight than expected for a fleece.',109,'2020-06-15'),(4408,'Beau B.',NULL,'5\'10 - 6\'0','L',NULL,5.0,'Love this! So versatile!','Love this! So versatile!',109,'2020-06-15'),(4409,'Tom B.',NULL,'None','M',NULL,5.0,'Like an old friend','I\'m a